overview: JD Marymee has been a 20+ year veteran in the computer industry with experience founding companies and running parts of large ones. He has founded or co-founded over six startups, some bootstrapped, some venture-backed. He has run evangelization teams, partner orgnaizations and large, distributed engineering groups. His experience with engineering covers Linux, Open Source, Windows, .NET, Java and web-based technologies (ASP, HTML5, JSP) as well as Databases (MySQL And SQL Server).
